Metadata-Version: 2.2
Name: authring
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Authring is an MCP-driven guardrails system that evaluates code modification proposals based on historical impact, contributor expertise, and production risk assessment. The system utilizes: Astra DB for historical data storage, Unstructured.io for document parsing, Langflow for AI-driven decision-making, Twilio for real-time human validation, and GitHub CLI (gh) for managing patch review links.
Author-email: Chris McKenzie <hello@noblox.pro>
